## 5. Assumptions
| ID | Assumption | Risk if Wrong |
|----|------------|--------------|
| A1 | Basic user identity and avatar fields are already modeled or will be modeled by backend within this task’s scope. | Profile editing may require schema changes and slip in schedule. |
| A2 | Media/storage for avatars is available via existing infrastructure. | Avatar upload might require additional infra work. |
| A3 | No complex privacy model is needed for MVP beyond simple “public vs not shown” profile fields. | Might require redesign of settings and visibility controls. |
| A4 | Navigation IA will remain relatively simple in this phase. | Later expansion could require refactoring nav layout. |

